dynamic "<block_type>" {
  for_each = <iterator>
  content {
    # what the <block_type> block should contain
  }
}


Use Case	
Repeat a block inside a resource (like ingress, tag, provisioner)	- Use dynamic block
Repeat the entire resource (like creating 3 EC2s or 5 S3 buckets)	- Use count or for_each


count = N times
for_each = list, map
dynamic = Block inside a resource



